Package: proscorer
Title: Scores commonly used patient-reported outcome (PRO) measures
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Ray Baser <baserr@mskcc.org> [aut,cre]",
    "Ayelet Greenbert <greenberg613@gmail.com> [ctb]"
    ))
Description: Provides functions to score commonly used patient-reported outcome
    (PRO) and quality of life (QOL) measures, including most of the Functional
    Assessment of Cancer Therapy (FACT) and Functional Assessment of Chronic
    Illness Therapy (FACIT) family of questionnaires.  The goal of this package
    is to serve as a free repository for accurate, reliable scoring algorithms
    for as many PRO and QOL instruments as possible, ultimately helping to
    improve the quality and reproducibility of PRO and QOL research.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.1)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
Suggests: knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
